title: Mythed Up
synopsis:
In a modern world where the barriers between the Supernatural and Natural vanished hundreds of years ago, seeing a centaur working as a personal trainer and a harpy running a courier service isn't out of the ordinary. Though, as in any version of our world, people are still people.


Updates every Wednesday

title: Golden Hour
synopsis: SLOW BURN/ROMANCE || Disgruntled, jaded and broke, Jeremiah is tired of the mundane life. His twenties are as dull as he can imagine, until a golden, excitable, four-legged friend decides to join him on his walk home. What Jeremiah doesn’t know is that his new furry companion would bring more than a few surprises, and among them being an unlikely friendship that will propel him into a whirlwind of emotions he did NOT sign up for. He can’t tell if it’s a good thing... only one way to find out.

title: Meme Girls
synopsis: Memes, gaming consoles, and websites turned into anime girls! Please enjoy this compilation of meme comics, oneshots, and shorts from the team behind Merryweather Comics!

title: Duncan and Eddie
synopsis: Two boyfriends stumbling their through life together. They may not be the most competent couple, but that won't stop them from loving each other to bits! Updates every SUNDAY

title: Falling In Love With My Ex-fiance's Grandfather
synopsis:
After getting rejected by her fiancé, 20-year old Mary Menoushire passed out from the shock. She then got possessed by a 50-year old lady from another world...who thinks her (ex)fiancé's grandfather is hotter.
#agegap #comedy

[Disclaimer: this comic started as a few jokes on Twitter. But since it got a lot of attention, I decided to make it a full-colored comic]

----updates Mon/Thurs----

title: type-blind
synopsis: Ryan has a type, and it isn't Dave. [BL] [Updates on Monday]

title: RUTHLESS (GL)
synopsis: (Updates every 8 days - 12 pm EST TIME) Seo Jimin lives by three rules, and a significant lesson from her parents, never get too close to anyone. She loves her independence, avoiding long-term connections. It’s all about the enjoyment without the relationship drama. This approach might get her a bad reputation at the university, but it prevents heartache, especially for her. Then, a strikingly beautiful neighbour arrives…

synopsis:

UPDATES TWICE A WEEK (18+ panels on Patreon)

title: My Boss Doesn't Have A Face
synopsis: Maya is the only one in the office who can't see her boss' face. In fear of being seen as insane, she has been keeping it a secret from everyone...until she slips up one day. Turns out, there is a big reason behind the condition. [DRAFT version]

title: The Weekly Roll
synopsis: A four-panel comic strip that follows the exploits of a party of adventurers as they walk the fine line between being the good guys and homeless psychopaths for hire.

title: Papercut Dreams (GL)
synopsis: What does it mean to have dreams? Shae, a young woman whose ambitions were shattered by a high school injury, now works as a barista to support her sick mother while her father steals her earnings. At 21, life feels like an endless struggle until a curious new neighbour challenges her perspective. Through this unexpected friendship, Shae begins to rediscover her dreams and the strength to pursue them.

title: Cherry Crush
synopsis:
[UPDATES EVERY FRIDAY/Midnight GMT-6]
Cherie, a 25 year-old salary worker, lives in a small apartment with his best friend, Crush. Cherie thought he could live forever with his secret crush on his roommate, but as events transpired, it proved to be a little difficult, especially when Crush's past is slowly catching up to him.
